Subject: Errors on Scanner/Zerologon test
Description:
When I run the  scanner/zerologon test within Ping Castle I get the following error in the resulting text file:

Error 2: c0000022

Do you know what that means?
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue 
Getting error when running the scanner/zerologon test 

Resolution 
the error means STATUS_ACCESS_DENIED (https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/openspecs/windows_protocols/ms-erref/596a1078-e883-4972-9bbc-49e60bebca55) which means that the mitigation against zero logon is active
